{"tid":2431022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"路透：梁振英不排除復出做特首　「盡一切努力為香港、国家服務」","createTime":"2021-03-03T10:47:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T12:01:36.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"081567afd52deb225ab379d8ebfddc975376e4f5","tid":2431022,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T10:47:36.000Z","msg":"全國政協副主席梁振英今（３日）接受路透社訪問，被問到會否不排除再次參選特首時，梁振英稱，「我會盡一切努力為香港服務，為國家服務。」<br />\n<br />\n梁振英在2012年特首選舉中，以689票當選特首，任內發生反國教事件、雨傘運動、旺角騷亂等事件。直至2016年12月9日，梁振英宣布因家庭原因，放棄爭取連任，任期至2017年6月30日完結。<br />\n<br />\n去年11月，梁振英接受港台節目《視點31》訪問時，被問到會否再參選特首，他直指：「目前無。」<br />\n<br />\n直至今年1月，梁振英接受訪問時表示，《中英聯合聲明》及《基本法》均清楚列明，香港特區行政長官可通過選舉或協商產生，並由中央政府任命，「若明天宣布特首改由協商產生，英國人不能說我們違反《中英聯合聲明》，亦不需修改《基本法》及人大釋法」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210303/443853943026487296394725.jpeg/jnoA4j8QmN5QArPRCKlTtitCK-khLNyqfZqlGn2apRo?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210303%2F443853943026487296394725.jpeg%2FjnoA4j8QmN5QArPRCKlTtitCK-khLNyqfZqlGn2apRo%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=845629d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.hk01 .com/政情/594508</code></pre>"},{"pid":"02afb7ef163c90457329c2702b47b9e3d3093214","tid":2431022,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T10:51:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YP1BMj2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYP1BMj2.jpg&h=b120be1b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d31fd40ce63508b4d270634dd83cb3bf1bc7fdb9","tid":2431022,"uid":180302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T10:52:26.000Z","msg":"目前無<br />\n即係有"},{"pid":"75c8564a8904be28dc2e15b3da1f7d54463bea7a","tid":2431022,"uid":18477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"02afb7ef163c90457329c2702b47b9e3d3093214","tid":2431022,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021